<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://static.topcv.vn/v4/image/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./asset/font/fontawesome-free-6.7.1-web/fontawesome-free-6.7.1-web/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/viecLam.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/dangnhap.css">
    <title>Chào mừng bạn đã quay trở lại | Topcv.vn</title>
</head>
<body>
    @{
        var email = Context.Session.GetString("email") ?? "";
    }
    <div class="main">
        <div class="login-box">
            <h2>Chào mừng bạn đã quay trở lại</h2>
            <p>Cùng xây dựng một hồ sơ nổi bật và nhận được các cơ hội sự nghiệp lý tưởng</p>
            <form action="@Url.Action("Index", "DangNhap")">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Email" name="email" required value="@email">
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="password">Mật khẩu</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Mật khẩu" name="matKhau" required>
                </div>
                <!-- Thêm radio buttons -->
                <div class="input-group">
                    <div class="radio-group">
                        <div class="item">
                            <input type="radio" name="userType" value="candidate" checked>
                            <label>
                                Ứng cử viên
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="item">
                            <input type="radio" name="userType" value="recruiter">
                            <label>
                                Nhà tuyển dụng
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="error">@ViewBag.Error</div>
                <a href="#" class="forgot-password">Quên mật khẩu</a>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Đăng nhập</button>
            </form>
            <p class="register">Bạn chưa có tài khoản? <a href="@Url.Action("Index","DangKyTaiKhoan")">Đăng ký ngay</a></p>
            <p class="support">Bạn gặp khó khăn khi tạo tài khoản? Vui lòng gọi tới số <strong>(024) 6680 5588</strong> (giờ hành chính).</p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="icon">
            <img src="https://static.topcv.vn/v4/image/auth/topcv_white.png" alt="TopCV Icon">
            <img class="arrow" src="https://static.topcv.vn/v4/image/auth/auth_arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon">
        </div>
        <h1>Tiếp lợi thế<br>Nối thành công</h1>
        <p>TopCV - Hệ sinh thái nhân sự tiên phong ứng dụng công nghệ tại Việt Nam</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>